data.description: This charming home features an open floor plan, three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a surrounding eat-in bar that is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying casual meals with your loved ones. The kitchen comes with a tile backsplash that adds a touch of elegance to the kitchen, making it a delight to prepare your favorite dishes.    The primary bedroom is spacious and features a walk-in closet, providing plenty of storage space for your wardrobe. Convenience is key, as this property includes a washer, dryer, and refrigerator.      Additionally, there's an extra room that can be utilized as a den or office, allowing you to create a space that suits your needs and lifestyle.    Located in a desirable neighborhood, this property offers easy access to nearby amenities such as a community pool, parks, schools, shopping centers, and restaurants.     Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home.
